<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Buyers in Kelvin Grove are typically professionals, academics and healthcare workers connected to QUT, RBWH and the city's professional core. Character home buyers know exactly what they are looking for: a Queenslander or Federation home with authenticity intact and scope for tasteful improvement, on a block large enough to justify the position. The Urban Village apartment buyers are younger professionals who want walkability and contemporary finish over period character. Both segments are active and well-researched, and well-positioned properties in either category consistently attract competitive enquiry.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Kelvin Grove State College is one of Brisbane's best-regarded selective state high schools, and its presence creates a consistent family buyer demand that runs alongside the professional market. Families who have secured a place at KGSC treat the catchment as a structural consideration, and homes within comfortable walking or cycling distance of the school attract a premium from that segment. Roma Street Parkland, the Herston medical precinct and the Inner City Bypass all shape the suburb's geography and the value within different pockets.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Kelvin Grove Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Character and Urban Village</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">QUT precinct, professional buyers</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/spring-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Spring Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/paddington" style="color:#c4912a;">Paddington</a>, <a href="/suburbs/red-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Red Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/ashgrove" style="color:#c4912a;">Ashgrove</a>.</p>
