    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Kelvin Grove.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Kelvin Grove?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kelvin Grove property values vary considerably with land size, position and dwelling type. Character homes on larger blocks consistently outperform the suburb median, while the Urban Village apartment and townhouse market reflects demand from QUT-adjacent professional buyers. An appraisal will give you the precise current picture.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Kelvin Grove?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented character homes in Kelvin Grove typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The suburb draws a focused professional buyer pool from the QUT precinct and nearby CBD, and properties at defensible prices rarely sit without strong enquiry.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Kelvin Grove?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kelvin Grove offers a genuinely urban lifestyle with character-suburb bones. The Urban Village at QUT has a pedestrian-scale precinct with cafes, galleries and community spaces. Roma Street Parkland is within easy walking distance, and the CBD is a 10-minute drive or short bus ride.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What types of homes are in Kelvin Grove?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kelvin Grove has one of Brisbane's more varied housing mixes: traditional Queenslanders and Federation-era homes on generous character-street blocks, alongside contemporary Urban Village apartments and townhouses built from the early 2000s onwards. Both segments attract distinct buyer profiles and consistent demand.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

